WEBVTT

01:37.060 --> 01:41.000
[The Best Thing]

01:41.250 --> 01:48.750
[Episode 9: Honey;
Sweet in taste, neutral in nature, supports digestion, moistens dryness, relieves pain, helps with detoxification, and promotes wound healing when used externally]

01:49.100 --> 01:50.350
[Oncology Ward]

02:13.760 --> 02:14.240
Hello.

02:14.800 --> 02:17.460
May I know if Dr. He Suye is here?

02:17.730 --> 02:18.520
Who are you?

02:18.550 --> 02:19.440
What are you looking him for?

02:20.270 --> 02:21.280
I'm his friend.

02:21.280 --> 02:22.430
I have something to give him.

02:24.340 --> 02:25.710
He's in Room 0405.

02:26.400 --> 02:27.120
It's right over there.

02:27.710 --> 02:28.710
Please wait at the door for a moment.

02:28.870 --> 02:30.079
The patients are resting.

02:30.190 --> 02:31.150
Okay, thank you.

02:37.120 --> 02:37.590
Who is it?

02:37.590 --> 02:38.360
Someone's looking for Dr. He.

02:38.840 --> 02:39.710
I don't recognize her.

02:39.960 --> 02:41.079
Could she be a patient's family member?

02:41.240 --> 02:42.000
I haven't seen her before.

02:59.970 --> 03:00.800
-Dr. He.
-Dad!

03:06.030 --> 03:06.870
Dad!

03:08.560 --> 03:09.610
Why are you running so fast?

03:09.640 --> 03:10.520
Where did you go to play?

03:10.560 --> 03:11.630
I went to the toy store.

03:12.560 --> 03:13.710
Come with me on my house calls this afternoon, okay?

03:14.360 --> 03:15.430
Come on, let's wash our hands first.

03:21.079 --> 03:21.710
Dad?

03:22.840 --> 03:23.400
Dad?

03:35.410 --> 03:36.040
Go.

03:36.290 --> 03:37.079
Go back to the ward first.

03:44.240 --> 03:46.710
Dr. He, you left your contract behind.

03:48.760 --> 03:49.520
I'm sorry.

03:49.950 --> 03:51.280
I was in a rush earlier.

03:52.290 --> 03:53.450
Did you take the contract with you?

04:05.330 --> 04:06.930
I'm here by the nurses' station.

04:07.230 --> 04:08.010
Come and get it.

04:28.410 --> 04:29.730
Thank you for making a special trip.

04:30.360 --> 04:31.000
Actually,

04:31.000 --> 04:32.630
you could have waited until I got back tonight

04:32.630 --> 04:33.600
to get it from you.

04:33.850 --> 04:34.920
It's okay.

04:34.920 --> 04:35.630
It's not trouble at all.

04:35.630 --> 04:36.920
I'm just glad you got it.

04:37.340 --> 04:38.220
Thank you.

04:38.240 --> 04:40.560
If there's nothing else, I'll head back to work.

04:41.140 --> 04:41.900
Bye.

04:51.310 --> 04:53.480
Dr. He, is there something going on?

04:55.150 --> 04:55.980
There's nothing going on.

04:56.630 --> 04:57.920
You said to get it when you go back tonight.

04:57.920 --> 04:58.890
How is this 'nothing going on"?

05:01.310 --> 05:02.240
Here you go.

05:15.110 --> 05:15.640
How's it going?

05:15.670 --> 05:16.900
There are still 35 patients to see.

05:16.920 --> 05:17.840
Alright, good work.

05:18.930 --> 05:19.800
Senior He.

05:20.270 --> 05:21.760
A girl came looking for you just now.

05:23.660 --> 05:24.540
I saw her.

05:26.130 --> 05:27.370
So who is she?

05:28.920 --> 05:29.960
A friend of mine.

05:31.400 --> 05:32.159
By the way,

05:32.490 --> 05:33.610
are you guys free on Sunday?

05:33.640 --> 05:35.640
Would you be interested in doing a project with me at a hotel?

05:35.960 --> 05:38.350
We'll design a TCM therapy package for them.

05:38.720 --> 05:39.800
There'll be extra pay.

05:40.690 --> 05:42.610
We just need to stay in the hotel, right?

05:43.330 --> 05:44.620
What a great opportunity!

05:44.650 --> 05:45.409
I want to go!

05:45.430 --> 05:46.520
Then I'll go too.

05:46.990 --> 05:48.550
But the place is far away in the suburbs.

05:48.600 --> 05:50.310
So you two need to come to my place on the weekend,

05:50.310 --> 05:51.390
and I'll drive you there.

05:51.390 --> 05:51.800
Okay.

05:52.870 --> 05:53.750
Which hotel is it?

05:56.980 --> 05:57.930
Gunan Huating.

05:59.720 --> 06:00.450
What's wrong?

06:02.680 --> 06:05.290
I suddenly remembered I might have something to do on Sunday.

06:05.560 --> 06:06.510
I can't make it.

06:08.620 --> 06:09.870
You two figure it out yourselves.

06:12.880 --> 06:13.560
Wait a minute.

06:13.990 --> 06:15.750
You just said you'll be free on Sunday

06:15.770 --> 06:16.940
to accompany me to the library.

06:22.160 --> 06:22.930
Did I say that?

06:25.510 --> 06:27.040
I've finalised the contract.

06:27.040 --> 06:28.730
He can start working here on Sunday.

06:28.830 --> 06:30.310
He'll also bring a few graduate students with him

06:30.310 --> 06:31.800
to work on this project together.

06:32.210 --> 06:32.760
Okay.

06:33.270 --> 06:34.600
Thanks for making the trip.

06:35.310 --> 06:35.920
Senior Lin,

06:36.620 --> 06:37.940
in our budget,

06:37.970 --> 06:39.720
is there any allowance for hospitality expenses?

06:40.630 --> 06:42.830
Why? Does Dr. He need to be reimbursed for transportation?

06:45.250 --> 06:46.159
Not really.

06:46.720 --> 06:49.240
I just want to give him a welcome gift.

06:49.870 --> 06:51.070
A welcome gift?

06:51.680 --> 06:52.360
That's fine.

06:52.930 --> 06:54.450
What kind of welcome gift do you want to give him?

06:58.120 --> 06:59.240
Children's toys.

07:00.510 --> 07:01.950
Dr. He plays with children's toys?

07:03.650 --> 07:05.090
Dr. He's son plays.

07:14.280 --> 07:16.120
When did you find out he has a child?

07:18.290 --> 07:21.010
I saw a little boy at the hospital today

07:21.040 --> 07:23.360
following him around and calling him 'Dad.'

07:24.230 --> 07:25.470
You two have known each other for months

07:25.500 --> 07:26.740
and he has never mentioned it to you?

07:27.280 --> 07:28.890
Could it be that he's already married?

07:30.940 --> 07:32.750
But I don't see him wearing a ring.

07:34.090 --> 07:35.510
So he's divorced.

07:36.720 --> 07:40.280
Indeed, all the handsome guys these days get married young.

07:44.320 --> 07:45.000
Xiangya.

07:45.720 --> 07:46.190
Do you think

07:46.190 --> 07:47.950
little boys would prefer

07:47.950 --> 07:50.070
these Transformers toys,

07:50.070 --> 07:53.040
or remote-controlled car models?

07:53.240 --> 07:54.680
How would I know?

07:58.390 --> 08:00.190
Oh, I just remembered.

08:01.310 --> 08:03.750
The other day when I taught him how to fold towel animals,

08:03.750 --> 08:05.630
I mentioned kids must really love them,

08:05.630 --> 08:06.920
and he seemed super interested.

08:07.750 --> 08:08.720
That's it.

08:08.720 --> 08:09.390
How many single men nowadays

08:09.390 --> 08:10.870
actually like children?

08:10.870 --> 08:12.720
He must have a child of his own.

08:23.450 --> 08:24.300
Are you off work?

08:25.000 --> 08:25.850
Come and have some medicinal food.

08:26.740 --> 08:28.500
I've made a soup with angelica, astragalus, and crucian carp.

08:34.039 --> 08:35.120
He texted me.

08:37.750 --> 08:39.630
He even invited you to his house for dinner.

08:39.630 --> 08:41.130
This cunning old man

08:41.159 --> 08:43.429
obviously wants you to be his son's stepmother.

08:43.450 --> 08:44.850
Quickly turn him down.

08:51.590 --> 08:54.110
I've already eaten. I appreciate the gesture.

08:54.790 --> 08:55.640
Thank you.

08:55.660 --> 08:57.090
You're being too polite.

08:57.120 --> 08:58.450
You should be more assertive.

08:58.980 --> 08:59.750
No.

08:59.750 --> 09:01.200
We still have to work together on Sunday.

09:01.200 --> 09:03.080
What happens if everyone feels awkward then?

09:03.080 --> 09:04.150
Alright, alright.

09:04.370 --> 09:05.770
Just pick one at random then.

09:06.080 --> 09:08.000
No need to waste time on this kind of thing.

09:28.080 --> 09:29.680
You've eaten so early?

09:58.200 --> 09:59.930
Grandpa, what are you doing?

09:59.960 --> 10:01.350
I'm about to have my meal.

10:01.660 --> 10:04.540
Making phone calls while eating is bad for your spleen and stomach.

10:04.570 --> 10:05.690
I have something to tell you.

10:06.630 --> 10:08.790
Call me back after I finish eating.

10:08.910 --> 10:09.550
Wait.

10:10.400 --> 10:11.400
This Sunday,

10:11.740 --> 10:13.340
I won't be coming over to your place.

10:14.080 --> 10:15.030
What are you going to do?

10:15.250 --> 10:16.680
I took on a consulting job.

10:17.040 --> 10:19.090
I'm working with the hotel Shen Xifan works for.

10:20.230 --> 10:22.780
I plan to take them to visit the herbal garden.

10:23.060 --> 10:24.900
Their hotel is quite close to the herbal garden.

10:24.920 --> 10:25.590
Is that okay?

10:25.630 --> 10:26.440
Sure, that's fine.

10:26.620 --> 10:27.820
It's our own garden after all.

10:27.870 --> 10:29.870
Just let the housekeeper know tomorrow.

10:32.010 --> 10:32.820
Wait.

10:33.370 --> 10:34.440
Shen Xifan?

10:35.750 --> 10:36.710
Yes, yes.

10:36.730 --> 10:38.420
Is that the young Miss Shen?

10:39.510 --> 10:41.940
Is it purely work-related?

10:42.030 --> 10:42.510
Or...

10:42.510 --> 10:44.050
I'm already so busy with work at the hospital.

10:44.120 --> 10:45.970
Why would I take on a purely work-related job?

10:47.440 --> 10:48.910
But you told me last time

10:48.910 --> 10:50.790
that young Miss Shen was about to get married.

10:53.250 --> 10:54.530
I was mistaken about that.

10:57.300 --> 10:58.820
So you've figured it out this time?

10:59.550 --> 11:00.790
What do you mean by "figured it out"?

11:01.140 --> 11:02.660
Are you referring to work or to her?

11:02.690 --> 11:04.010
Don't play dumb.

11:04.050 --> 11:06.080
I'm talking about her, Shen Xifan.

11:10.080 --> 11:10.920
Yes, I've figured it out.

11:11.290 --> 11:13.220
Well, she's a smart

11:13.490 --> 11:15.330
and interesting girl.

11:15.360 --> 11:17.360
And she's quite childlike as well.

11:17.440 --> 11:18.510
Childlike?

11:20.400 --> 11:21.920
In your fifty years of medical practice,

11:21.940 --> 11:23.900
have you ever met a patient who haggled with you

11:23.930 --> 11:25.410
and even altered your prescription?

11:25.430 --> 11:26.640
Who would dare?

11:26.670 --> 11:27.270
She did.

11:29.150 --> 11:29.870
Alright then.

11:30.410 --> 11:32.290
You handle it as you see fit.

11:33.840 --> 11:35.510
You've been presumptuous for so long,

11:35.840 --> 11:37.440
it's time to make an effort.

11:37.840 --> 11:40.120
Girls need to be pursued.

11:42.640 --> 11:43.730
Okay, got it.

11:44.050 --> 11:45.210
That's all then. Bye-bye.

12:04.270 --> 12:05.790
What's with that expression?

12:06.720 --> 12:07.870
Let me tell you,

12:08.790 --> 12:10.480
all men are the same.

12:11.030 --> 12:13.320
No matter how nice they seem on the surface,

12:14.240 --> 12:16.630
they're always singing a different tune inside.

12:18.080 --> 12:19.630
Only people like me...

12:20.720 --> 12:21.960
Only people like you

12:22.290 --> 12:24.680
who've been sheltered all their lives

12:25.270 --> 12:26.510
would fall for their tricks.

12:27.670 --> 12:29.880
Look at Lin Yishen, is he any good?

12:30.310 --> 12:32.550
He's always smiling,

12:32.630 --> 12:33.670
treating girls extra gently

12:33.670 --> 12:34.870
and being overly attentive.

12:35.070 --> 12:37.020
And then there's your ex-boyfriend, Yan Heng.

12:39.380 --> 12:41.500
He was so cold and abusive before the breakup,

12:42.150 --> 12:43.990
making it seem like it was all your fault.

12:45.150 --> 12:46.540
In reality, he wanted to break up long ago.

12:47.450 --> 12:48.780
He just couldn't find an excuse.

12:49.270 --> 12:51.270
And here you are, making excuses for him,

12:51.270 --> 12:52.520
and trying to find reasons within yourself.

12:52.550 --> 12:53.340
You...

12:53.360 --> 12:54.410
Enough, enough, enough.

12:54.440 --> 12:55.600
Stop talking about Yan Heng.

12:55.910 --> 12:57.030
The more you talk, the sadder I feel.

12:57.030 --> 12:57.790
Stop.

12:58.110 --> 12:59.960
Alright, I'll get straight to the point.

13:00.600 --> 13:02.320
If a woman wants to live well,

13:03.110 --> 13:05.200
she absolutely cannot waste energy on self-consuming.

13:05.200 --> 13:07.110
All the faults lie with others.

13:27.750 --> 13:28.590
Hello, welcome.

13:45.560 --> 13:47.230
Hello, where are they?

13:47.230 --> 13:47.630
There.

13:51.230 --> 13:52.080
Thanks.

14:00.630 --> 14:01.350
Xifan.

14:02.510 --> 14:03.280
Xifan.

14:04.400 --> 14:05.200
Xifan.

14:06.590 --> 14:07.080
Xifan.

14:09.470 --> 14:10.440
I'm sorry.

14:11.600 --> 14:12.960
How much did you drink?

14:14.010 --> 14:14.850
Pack up your things.

14:14.870 --> 14:16.060
I'll send you home.

14:17.510 --> 14:18.750
How much did you drink?

14:19.000 --> 14:20.590
Xiangya, Xiangya.

14:20.630 --> 14:22.080
Xu Xiangya.

14:23.110 --> 14:23.920
Get up, let's go.

14:23.920 --> 14:24.510
Pack up, I'll send you home.

14:24.510 --> 14:25.750
Why is it you?

14:26.200 --> 14:27.110
What do you mean "why is it me"?

14:27.110 --> 14:28.590
You called me to come here.

14:28.830 --> 14:30.750
Get up, pack your things, I'll send you home.

14:30.750 --> 14:31.280
Really?

14:31.490 --> 14:32.230
Hurry up.

14:33.230 --> 14:34.110
Trash.

14:36.630 --> 14:38.920
Trash who doesn't even know he's trash.

14:40.470 --> 14:42.470
The trash guy they've been cursing all this time,

14:42.470 --> 14:43.470
-it's him?
-How much did you drink?

14:43.470 --> 14:43.870
Get up quickly.

14:43.870 --> 14:45.400
Let's go.

14:46.830 --> 14:47.960
Let me tell you,

14:47.960 --> 14:49.990
you'd better apologize to me when you're sober tomorrow.

14:52.530 --> 14:53.410
Xifan.

14:53.440 --> 14:54.160
Don't move yet.

14:54.160 --> 14:55.560
I'll send you all back together.

14:55.870 --> 14:57.400
No need, I've called a car.

14:57.400 --> 14:58.870
You can just send Xiangya home.

14:59.470 --> 15:00.960
Get up, get up.

15:01.400 --> 15:02.110
Don't call a car.

15:02.110 --> 15:02.980
I'll send you home.

15:03.010 --> 15:03.970
I've already called.

15:04.560 --> 15:05.210
I...

15:06.870 --> 15:07.350
Xifan,

15:07.350 --> 15:08.350
your things!

15:53.090 --> 15:54.520
I'm home.

16:20.440 --> 16:21.560
Shen Xifan?

16:22.390 --> 16:23.670
Why are you sitting here all by yourself?

16:29.280 --> 16:30.320
What are you doing?

16:31.320 --> 16:33.400
So you didn't come for dinner because you went drinking.

16:34.500 --> 16:35.780
Come on, let's get you home.

16:36.280 --> 16:37.590
Don't worry about me.

16:39.680 --> 16:41.320
You'll catch a cold if you stay out here in the wind.

16:43.830 --> 16:44.190
What?

16:44.220 --> 16:44.740
Trash.

16:44.870 --> 16:45.320
I...

16:45.320 --> 16:46.020
Not replying to WeChat messages

16:46.050 --> 16:47.020
is trash.

16:47.280 --> 16:49.750
Treating others to meals is also trash.

16:49.750 --> 16:51.200
Look, there's trash everywhere.

16:51.200 --> 16:51.960
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven.

16:51.960 --> 16:52.870
I'm trash, I'm trash.

16:52.870 --> 16:53.510
I'll send you home.

16:53.510 --> 16:54.750
You're not allowed to send me home.

16:54.750 --> 16:55.400
What are you doing?

16:55.400 --> 16:56.560
I'm not even drunk.

16:56.560 --> 16:57.350
How is this not drunk?

16:57.350 --> 16:58.040
You're not sober.

16:58.040 --> 16:59.110
I'm not drunk.

17:00.520 --> 17:01.610
Your behavior when drunk.

17:05.550 --> 17:06.790
Don't you dare follow me.

17:09.710 --> 17:10.839
I'm watching you.

17:33.400 --> 17:35.230
Mr. Shen, Ms. Liu,

17:35.960 --> 17:38.200
there's a man following me.

17:40.160 --> 17:41.360
The one with the bowl haircut.

17:41.360 --> 17:42.470
Go check it out quickly.

17:42.990 --> 17:44.530
-Are you alright?
-What a rogue!

17:44.860 --> 17:46.210
There are so many people in this neighbourhood.

17:46.310 --> 17:47.710
Aren't you too bold?

17:47.710 --> 17:48.880
If you don't leave, I'm calling the police.

17:49.180 --> 17:50.620
Get away right now.

17:51.330 --> 17:52.360
He was following you?

17:53.290 --> 17:55.000
Where did you go drinking?

17:55.070 --> 17:56.200
She went drinking.

17:56.500 --> 17:58.130
What's going on? Are you okay?

17:58.160 --> 17:59.050
I'm fine.

17:59.380 --> 18:00.510
Let's go, let's go.

18:01.070 --> 18:02.600
Let's go home too.

18:02.600 --> 18:03.880
Don't come back so late.

18:03.880 --> 18:04.790
Be careful of your safety.

18:05.680 --> 18:07.510
You're quite fierce when you're drunk.

18:08.400 --> 18:09.610
Little drunkard.

18:26.470 --> 18:27.470
My head hurts.

18:29.310 --> 18:30.750
I'm never drinking again.

18:50.710 --> 18:52.090
I've taken the toys for you, okay?

19:00.550 --> 19:04.480
[Come for your follow-up visit anytime. No need to register.]

19:00.550 --> 19:04.480
[Are you awake? Remember to come for your follow-up visit. Go have some fruits when you wake up. Drinking more honey water helps with the hangover.]

19:14.840 --> 19:17.550
"Come for your follow-up visit anytime. No need to register."

19:19.360 --> 19:20.120
Trash.

19:20.350 --> 19:21.830
Not replying to WeChat messages is trash.

19:21.920 --> 19:23.600
Treating others to meals is also trash.

19:23.600 --> 19:24.030
Okay.

19:24.030 --> 19:25.470
-One, two, three, four, five, six, seven.
-I’m trash. I’m trash.

19:25.470 --> 19:25.960
I'll send you home.

19:25.960 --> 19:27.400
You're not allowed to send me home.

19:34.540 --> 19:35.370
It's over.

19:36.110 --> 19:37.700
I'm the real trash.

20:05.400 --> 20:06.330
You're up?

20:06.350 --> 20:07.620
Good morning.

20:07.650 --> 20:08.860
Morning.

20:29.960 --> 20:32.400
Throwing it away when it's perfectly fine is such a waste.

21:42.620 --> 21:44.380
I got a stiff neck from sleeping on the couch.

21:54.680 --> 21:56.370
Why did you scold me last night?

21:58.960 --> 21:59.960
Did I scold you?

22:00.130 --> 22:01.100
Yes, you did.

22:01.120 --> 22:03.390
You called me trash who doesn't know they're trash.

22:07.470 --> 22:08.710
I might have...

22:09.080 --> 22:10.710
mistaken you for someone else when I was drunk.

22:15.920 --> 22:17.510
I've noticed lately

22:17.510 --> 22:19.070
you've been acting passive-aggressive towards me.

22:19.070 --> 22:20.090
What did I do to you?

22:22.750 --> 22:24.120
Is it because of the Goddess Group incident?

22:25.090 --> 22:25.850
No.

22:26.360 --> 22:27.200
Then why?

22:34.750 --> 22:35.790
I just don't like you.

22:36.310 --> 22:36.920
Hold on.

22:37.690 --> 22:40.250
You must have a reason for not liking me, right?

22:44.030 --> 22:45.550
Tell me what you don't like about me then.

22:45.550 --> 22:47.310
I'll change. I'll apologize to you.

22:54.640 --> 22:56.310
Are you going back to your hometown soon?

23:08.710 --> 23:09.680
How did you know?

23:11.030 --> 23:12.750
I overheard you talking on the phone with your mom.

23:17.230 --> 23:17.880
So you heard.

23:17.880 --> 23:18.880
Why didn't you ask me about it?

23:23.270 --> 23:24.160
Why should I ask you?

23:24.160 --> 23:25.550
You weren't planning to tell me anyway.

23:26.230 --> 23:28.410
Since you didn't say anything, I'll just pretend I don't know.

23:32.200 --> 23:33.200
I'm done eating. I'm going now.

23:33.200 --> 23:34.720
Wait, let's clear things up before you go.

23:37.310 --> 23:39.030
Someone's treating me to a big meal later.

23:39.880 --> 23:40.990
I need to get dressed up.

23:41.290 --> 23:42.770
Leave on your own when you're done eating.

24:00.400 --> 24:02.070
Do you need it heated up?

24:41.750 --> 24:42.840
Xiangya.

24:44.070 --> 24:44.680
Tomorrow, you

24:44.680 --> 24:46.680
should at least treat me to two meals.

25:22.960 --> 25:24.360
Still not awake yet, huh?

25:32.880 --> 25:34.790
What time are we going to the hotel tomorrow?

25:34.990 --> 25:36.230
Do you need me to drive you there?

25:42.040 --> 25:44.470
10 in the morning. I can take the bus there.

25:44.710 --> 25:45.360
Thank you.

25:56.510 --> 25:57.200
Okay.

26:33.070 --> 26:34.070
We're here.

26:39.230 --> 26:40.880
Your Highness, please exit the car.

26:41.230 --> 26:42.230
Thank you, Prince.

26:58.550 --> 26:59.550
Hello, Dr. He.

26:59.710 --> 27:00.230
Hello.

27:00.230 --> 27:01.750
I'm the manager of the Marketing Department at our hotel,

27:01.750 --> 27:02.470
Lin Yishen.

27:02.470 --> 27:04.600
I'm also the person in charge of this project.

27:05.270 --> 27:05.680
Nice to meet you.

27:05.880 --> 27:06.470
Nice to meet you.

27:07.090 --> 27:07.850
Let me intro-

27:13.640 --> 27:14.640
Let me introduce you.

27:15.230 --> 27:16.990
This is Xu Xiangya, the manager of our Food & Beverage Department.

27:19.920 --> 27:21.400
I don't need to introduce Manager Shen in detail, do I?

27:21.400 --> 27:23.000
No need, we know each other well.

27:35.070 --> 27:36.600
These are my two postgraduate students.

27:36.600 --> 27:38.440
They're taking this chance to learn.

27:42.510 --> 27:43.790
This is Li Jie.

27:44.570 --> 27:45.890
You two have met before, right?

27:52.830 --> 27:54.760
We've met in the hospital lobby.

27:56.270 --> 27:57.510
I remember.

27:58.620 --> 28:00.170
-Nice to meet you.
-Nice to meet you.

28:01.180 --> 28:02.790
This is my junior, Fang Kexin.

28:03.090 --> 28:03.940
Hello.

28:04.490 --> 28:06.610
You were the one who gave me directions at the hospital, right?

28:06.880 --> 28:07.680
Yes.

28:07.890 --> 28:08.850
-Hello.
-Hello.

28:09.400 --> 28:11.090
Welcome, please come in.

28:12.400 --> 28:14.130
Manager Shen, I-

28:14.660 --> 28:15.500
Mo.

28:15.900 --> 28:17.590
Please park the car for Dr. He.

28:17.620 --> 28:18.300
Okay.

28:18.710 --> 28:19.360
Hello, sir.

28:19.550 --> 28:20.510
You just need to pass me the car keys.

28:22.640 --> 28:23.310
Please give them to me.

28:23.310 --> 28:23.880
Thank you.

28:24.710 --> 28:26.230
He is indeed quite handsome.

28:26.910 --> 28:28.150
Unfortunately, he's not suitable.

28:45.420 --> 28:48.110
Thank you all for taking the time to come here today.

28:48.440 --> 28:48.920
Here.

28:49.200 --> 28:50.310
This is a small token of our appreciation.

28:50.310 --> 28:51.360
Thank you.

28:51.960 --> 28:52.550
Thank you.

28:52.550 --> 28:53.030
You're welcome.

28:53.510 --> 28:54.120
Thank you.

28:55.160 --> 28:56.030
Please, this way.

29:01.310 --> 29:02.780
[Robot model]

29:23.470 --> 29:25.310
If the elderly experience insomnia,

29:25.310 --> 29:26.120
we can improve their sleep conditions

29:26.120 --> 29:28.120
through massaging their Yintang

29:28.120 --> 29:29.310
and Baihui acupoints.

29:29.770 --> 29:31.090
Massaging these two acupoints

29:31.160 --> 29:32.920
can have a calming and sedative effect.

29:33.200 --> 29:34.200
The massage technique

29:34.840 --> 29:36.750
is roughly as demonstrated by Fang.

29:38.580 --> 29:40.890
The Baihui acupoint is at the midpoint of the line connecting the ears,

29:41.160 --> 29:43.180
while the Yintang acupoint is at the centre between the eyebrows.

29:44.060 --> 29:45.540
This is a relatively simple

29:45.640 --> 29:47.750
and effective massaging technique.

29:49.230 --> 29:50.510
The hotel staff

29:50.510 --> 29:52.120
can learn it through simple practice

29:52.120 --> 29:52.920
and quickly master it.

29:56.430 --> 29:57.670
Let me try.

30:03.680 --> 30:04.440
Go ahead.

30:04.880 --> 30:05.840
This position.

30:07.110 --> 30:08.790
Then use this hand to support him.

30:08.820 --> 30:09.580
Put your hand here.

30:09.600 --> 30:10.190
Right.

30:10.840 --> 30:13.030
Then use this hand to support him on this side.

30:13.030 --> 30:14.200
In the TCM theory,

30:14.200 --> 30:17.680
insomnia and frequent dreams are often due to emotional distress.

30:19.200 --> 30:20.510
In most cases,

30:20.850 --> 30:22.530
it's considered a heart issue.

30:23.710 --> 30:24.790
Because the heart houses the spirit.

30:25.400 --> 30:28.070
If the heart doesn't house the spirit, the spirit has no place to dwell

30:28.960 --> 30:29.790
and becomes restless,

30:30.840 --> 30:31.710
hence resulting in sleeplessness.

30:35.840 --> 30:36.990
I recommend using aromatherapy

30:37.360 --> 30:39.040
or adding some herbs with calming effects

30:39.070 --> 30:40.820
to buckwheat pillows.

30:41.790 --> 30:44.360
Using aromatherapy and buckwheat pillows to treat insomnia

30:44.890 --> 30:46.280
has a gentle and smooth effect

30:46.460 --> 30:47.460
and is more easily accepted.

30:49.200 --> 30:49.880
Not bad, not bad.

30:51.990 --> 30:53.990
These are some basic TCM knowledge.

30:53.990 --> 30:54.920
Do you have any questions?

31:16.770 --> 31:17.720
Did it turn red?

31:18.790 --> 31:19.710
No, no, no.

31:19.710 --> 31:20.360
A little bit.

31:21.530 --> 31:22.120
It's not noticeable.

31:22.120 --> 31:23.680
Alright, that's all for today's content.

31:23.680 --> 31:24.960
I hope it's helpful for everyone.

31:25.200 --> 31:26.400
It's very helpful.

31:26.470 --> 31:27.250
Thank you, thank you.

31:28.120 --> 31:29.400
Later, we'll organize our staff

31:29.400 --> 31:31.030
to watch the footage we just recorded

31:31.030 --> 31:32.790
to learn these massage techniques and knowledge.

31:33.270 --> 31:35.670
Do we have any other plans for this afternoon?

31:37.880 --> 31:39.200
Twenty minutes away from the hotel,

31:39.200 --> 31:40.840
there's an herbal plantation base

31:40.840 --> 31:42.190
that collaborates with our school.

31:42.360 --> 31:43.920
Actually, we could go and visit it.

31:44.270 --> 31:46.550
Meanwhile, we can use the readily available herbs from the base

31:46.550 --> 31:47.600
to make some samples.

31:47.790 --> 31:49.270
Alright, let's do that.

31:49.550 --> 31:51.600
So, that's it for this morning.

31:52.440 --> 31:53.840
Please, the three of you, head to the restaurant.

31:53.840 --> 31:54.880
We've prepared some of

31:54.880 --> 31:56.070
our hotel's signature dishes

31:56.070 --> 31:57.200
for you three to taste.

31:57.710 --> 31:58.370
-Let’s eat.
-Thank you.

31:59.210 --> 31:59.780
Let's go, let's go.

31:59.810 --> 32:00.850
It's time to eat.

32:01.920 --> 32:02.680
Xifan.

32:02.680 --> 32:03.070
Yes.

32:03.070 --> 32:03.920
Dr. He,

32:04.160 --> 32:05.880
I'll put the gift I gave you

32:05.880 --> 32:07.030
in your car.

32:07.030 --> 32:08.440
This way you won't have to carry it.

32:08.640 --> 32:09.440
No need to be polite.

32:09.990 --> 32:10.920
What I mean is...

32:25.230 --> 32:27.150
Why did she give me toys?

32:32.880 --> 32:36.300
[Yuncong All Day Dining Restaurant]

32:56.700 --> 32:59.020
Here comes our signature dish!

32:59.370 --> 33:02.240
Bamboo shoot and chicken stew.

33:05.920 --> 33:08.070
This chicken is grain-fed by local farmers.

33:08.070 --> 33:08.790
it's especially organic,

33:08.790 --> 33:09.750
and very healthy.

33:10.470 --> 33:13.170
The poached shrimp is both refreshing and sweet.

33:13.440 --> 33:16.930
And there's this black truffle cheese pizza.

33:16.960 --> 33:18.360
It's particularly popular among young people.

33:20.710 --> 33:21.470
Here you go.

33:22.380 --> 33:23.380
Kexin, have a slice.

33:24.640 --> 33:25.530
Thank you.

33:31.280 --> 33:33.390
Come on, little brother, try some.

33:36.630 --> 33:37.950
Okay, thank you.

33:42.990 --> 33:43.880
Is it good?

33:45.440 --> 33:46.610
This is really delicious!

33:47.470 --> 33:48.510
It's our exclusive recipe.

33:48.510 --> 33:49.750
You can't find it anywhere else.

33:53.270 --> 33:54.920
Come on, Dr. He. Grab a bite.

33:57.790 --> 33:58.460
Dr. He,

33:58.650 --> 34:00.300
I heard you're an oncologist from

34:00.320 --> 34:01.650
the the City TCM Hospital?

34:01.850 --> 34:02.370
Yes.

34:04.070 --> 34:04.840
then how come Xifan

34:04.840 --> 34:06.200
went to an oncologist

34:06.200 --> 34:07.310
to treat insomnia?

34:12.239 --> 34:14.760
I do consultations at a clinic near my home on weekends.

34:15.300 --> 34:17.530
She probably just happened to get an appointment with me.

34:18.920 --> 34:21.110
I was just getting an appointment randomly.

34:24.679 --> 34:25.690
Try this, brother.

34:26.070 --> 34:26.630
Okay.

34:36.179 --> 34:37.550
How did you think of

34:37.550 --> 34:39.030
the idea of giving me children's toys?

34:42.800 --> 34:44.030
Since you're a local,

34:44.760 --> 34:45.719
giving you local specialties

34:45.719 --> 34:46.540
doesn't seem appropriate.

34:46.650 --> 34:47.730
Gifting you health supplements instead

34:47.750 --> 34:49.620
might come across as showing off in front of experts.

34:50.080 --> 34:52.219
So I prepared a set of toys for your son

34:52.400 --> 34:53.400
to express my gratitude.

34:57.070 --> 34:58.650
Where did Senior He get a son from?

35:00.570 --> 35:01.600
Yeah.

35:01.990 --> 35:03.320
Are you sure you haven't made a mistake?

35:11.800 --> 35:12.470
Well...

35:14.280 --> 35:16.580
That day when I went to the hospital to find you,

35:17.070 --> 35:20.840
I saw a child about seven or eight years old...

35:21.110 --> 35:21.920
Dad!

35:22.560 --> 35:23.600
Why are you running so fast?

35:23.620 --> 35:24.540
Where did you run off to play?

35:24.800 --> 35:26.360
Following right behind you,

35:26.900 --> 35:29.390
calling you 'Dad'.

35:31.250 --> 35:33.080
You must be talking about Zhao Ze.

35:33.800 --> 35:35.760
He's a young patient at our hospital.

35:36.240 --> 35:38.720
He likes to call Senior He that way all the time.

35:39.330 --> 35:41.120
But he's not Senior He's son.

35:45.010 --> 35:47.940
Senior He is still single.

35:48.740 --> 35:50.410
I told him not to call me that randomly.

35:51.070 --> 35:52.220
So something did happen after all.

35:55.070 --> 35:56.230
I don't know...

36:09.670 --> 36:10.740
As long as you got it.

36:11.400 --> 36:12.360
I'm going back to work.

36:14.620 --> 36:15.370
Trash.

36:15.510 --> 36:15.840
I...

36:15.840 --> 36:17.490
Not replying to WeChat messages is trash.

36:17.880 --> 36:19.800
Treating others to meals is also trash.

36:19.800 --> 36:21.590
Look, there's trash everywhere.

36:21.590 --> 36:22.990
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven.

36:23.890 --> 36:26.080
I don't need to introduce Manager Shen in detail, do I?

36:45.790 --> 36:46.460
Let's eat.

36:49.150 --> 36:50.190
Try this.

37:07.830 --> 37:08.620
Xifan.

37:09.140 --> 37:09.500
Come on.

37:09.870 --> 37:13.240
♫No fear of the night, no matter how long♫

37:13.680 --> 37:17.070
♫Your voice is always gentle♫

37:17.490 --> 37:21.220
♫Knowing you'll wait for me to take that brave step♫

37:21.320 --> 37:23.540
♫Walking toward you♫

37:23.560 --> 37:27.000
♫At the end of my dreams♫

37:27.180 --> 37:31.000
♫Holding on tight, never letting go♫

37:31.290 --> 37:34.430
♫Waiting for you♫

37:34.760 --> 37:38.150
♫To heal every tomorrow for me♫

37:38.250 --> 37:41.900
♫The best time♫

37:47.690 --> 37:51.250
♫There's always something in the past♫

37:51.540 --> 37:55.150
♫We thought about it, but we seem to have forgotten it♫

37:55.330 --> 37:59.150
♫But those moments about you♫

37:59.180 --> 38:01.140
♫I remember everything♫

38:01.440 --> 38:05.090
♫I'm willing to be with you♫

38:05.290 --> 38:08.830
♫I'll go through every time and space with you♫

38:09.080 --> 38:13.620
♫And you are the reason♫

38:13.650 --> 38:16.930
♫I hold on to the moment so dearly♫

38:17.650 --> 38:21.390
♫No fear of the night, no matter how long♫

38:21.700 --> 38:25.210
♫Your voice is always gentle♫

38:25.460 --> 38:29.240
♫Knowing you'll wait for me to take that brave step♫

38:29.680 --> 38:31.680
♫Walking toward you♫

38:31.710 --> 38:35.080
♫At the end of my dreams♫

38:35.250 --> 38:38.930
♫Holding on tight, never letting go♫

38:39.250 --> 38:42.610
♫Waiting for you♫

38:41.550 --> 38:42.920
I was saying, that day after coming back from the hospital,

38:42.920 --> 38:44.920
why did you suddenly go drinking?

38:45.210 --> 38:47.000
So it was because you misunderstood Dr. He.

38:47.020 --> 38:48.710
That's why you went to drink your sorrows away.

38:50.600 --> 38:51.890
You've taken a liking to Dr. He?

38:54.830 --> 38:56.040
What if one day

38:56.070 --> 38:58.020
I suddenly have a son pop up out of nowhere,

38:58.040 --> 39:00.040
would you also go off drinking?

39:00.150 --> 39:01.360
Of course I would.

39:01.380 --> 39:02.380
What are you thinking?

39:02.800 --> 39:03.470
Alright, alright.

39:03.470 --> 39:05.720
I've noticed you're really stubborn.

39:07.170 --> 39:08.330
But seriously though,

39:08.360 --> 39:10.470
I think Dr. He is a good person.

39:10.550 --> 39:11.550
He has a nice personality too.

39:11.550 --> 39:12.920
And he's serious about his work.

39:12.920 --> 39:14.460
I think you could consider him.

39:14.490 --> 39:15.790
You don't need to have so many concerns.

39:20.300 --> 39:22.300
You're quite good at talking about others.

39:28.190 --> 39:29.030
Xifan.

39:29.890 --> 39:32.090
That student Dr. He is mentoring,

39:32.190 --> 39:33.470
that little boy.

39:34.220 --> 39:35.490
Can you give me his WeChat?

39:41.970 --> 39:45.000
I don't seem to have his WeChat.

39:45.030 --> 39:46.030
I don't believe you.

39:46.030 --> 39:48.190
I don't believe you just met at the hospital.

39:48.190 --> 39:49.280
I just saw him

39:49.280 --> 39:50.920
looking at you like this.

39:52.360 --> 39:53.840
Actually, the two of us

39:53.840 --> 39:55.440
met for the first time on a blind date.

39:55.440 --> 39:57.120
We just had afternoon tea and then parted ways.

39:57.200 --> 39:58.590
So we didn't exchange WeChat.

39:58.990 --> 40:00.720
And I didn't know at the time

40:00.720 --> 40:02.470
that he was Dr. He's student.

40:04.240 --> 40:04.990
Alright then.

40:05.800 --> 40:07.030
I'll add him myself.

40:07.510 --> 40:08.990
Anyway, for work reasons,

40:08.990 --> 40:11.150
adding him on WeChat makes sense, right?

40:12.670 --> 40:14.150
But to be honest,

40:14.150 --> 40:16.960
I think he probably likes He Suye.

40:16.960 --> 40:18.390
The other female student.

40:18.540 --> 40:21.230
Isn't it not so good for us to add him on WeChat like this?

40:21.250 --> 40:22.540
Is that his girlfriend?

40:26.380 --> 40:27.740
Probably not.

40:27.800 --> 40:29.280
Then it's settled, isn't it?

40:29.310 --> 40:31.060
I'll add him on WeChat first and then we'll see.

40:42.110 --> 40:43.630
Now I don't like domineering CEOs anymore.

40:43.630 --> 40:45.110
I prefer younger guys now.

40:47.840 --> 40:49.150
Young guys are so nice.

40:49.670 --> 40:50.760
they're simple-minded,

40:51.880 --> 40:53.150
and obedient and well-behaved.

40:53.660 --> 40:54.740
Unlike some people.

41:25.480 --> 41:26.890
You know what?

41:26.920 --> 41:27.440
it's so close,

41:27.440 --> 41:28.400
yet we never noticed

41:28.400 --> 41:29.800
such a nice place nearby.

41:30.960 --> 41:31.720
This herbal garden

41:31.720 --> 41:33.280
is our school's teaching base.

41:33.550 --> 41:35.240
It's usually not open to the public.

41:35.950 --> 41:37.760
only after freshmen enroll

41:37.800 --> 41:39.720
do we bring them here for a visit

41:39.720 --> 41:40.630
and some learning.

42:03.070 --> 42:04.760
So I said it's a rare opportunity.

42:04.780 --> 42:05.930
You should come and take a look.

42:15.730 --> 42:17.080
I'll take you inside for a tour,

42:17.110 --> 42:19.050
then we'll go back to the research lab to continue working.

42:19.090 --> 42:19.730
Okay,

42:20.290 --> 42:20.950
okay.

42:29.510 --> 42:30.880
This whole area is platycodon.

42:31.360 --> 42:33.400
It will be very beautiful when it blooms next year.

42:36.150 --> 42:38.550
Platycodon has effects of clearing the lungs, soothing the throat, and expelling phlegm.

42:38.550 --> 42:40.110
It can be used to treat coughs,

42:40.110 --> 42:41.270
excessive phlegm, and other symptoms.

42:44.400 --> 42:46.320
This patch is newly planted salvia.

42:46.640 --> 42:48.880
Planting in autumn yields a slightly better harvest.

42:50.110 --> 42:51.400
Is it the same salvia

42:51.400 --> 42:52.280
as in Salvia Miltiorrhiza Dropping Pills?

42:52.430 --> 42:53.070
Yes.

42:53.390 --> 42:54.390
It's growing quite well.

42:54.910 --> 42:55.470
What do you think?

42:55.490 --> 42:57.040
Not bad, right?
It’s a nice day.

42:57.630 --> 42:58.240
Indeed.

42:58.240 --> 42:58.630
So beautiful.

42:58.630 --> 42:59.990
The lighting here is really nice.

42:59.990 --> 43:00.590
How cute!

43:00.890 --> 43:02.440
Did you plant these flowers yourselves?

43:03.110 --> 43:03.880
They're wild.

43:04.300 --> 43:04.830
Dr. He,

43:04.860 --> 43:06.170
let's take a group photo.

43:06.930 --> 43:07.320
Let's not.

43:07.320 --> 43:08.190
It's okay,

43:08.190 --> 43:09.070
don't be shy.

43:09.070 --> 43:10.030
Come on,

43:10.350 --> 43:11.140
stand here.

43:11.190 --> 43:12.230
Come, stand right here.

43:12.380 --> 43:13.220
Stand here.

43:15.150 --> 43:15.670
Come on.

43:16.990 --> 43:17.590
Are we taking the photo or not?

43:20.800 --> 43:21.990
Look at the camera.

43:22.630 --> 43:23.070
Three,

43:23.100 --> 43:23.590
two,

43:23.590 --> 43:24.030
one,

43:24.380 --> 43:26.560
cheese!
